{
  "id": "adv_card_rui_04_02",
  "title": "天動瑠依 2話 自分の未熟さ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-02-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ファッションショーに向けて練習を始めて数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days after starting to practice for the fashion show",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "体のラインを意識して……こんな感じかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Concentrating on my body lines… Is this the right pose?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "にこっ……違うわね……\nスンっ……これもなんか違う……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ not like this…\nHmm‚ this feels off…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "何をしてるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you doing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "きゃあ！　{user}さん！？\nいつからそこに！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kyaa! {user}-san!?\nHow long have you been there!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "さっきからずっと見てたよ。自分を見つめて\nぶつぶつとつぶやいていたようだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've been watching you the whole time.\nYou were staring at yourself and muttering…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "自分の姿に見とれていた訳じゃないですからね！？\n私はナルシストじゃありませんから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wasn't staring at myself‚ you know!\nI'm not a narcissist!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "もう……見ていたのなら声を掛けて下さい……\n恥ずかしいです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you were watching‚ you should have said something…\nIt's embarrassing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ひょっとしてポージングの練習をしていたのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Were you practicing posing by any chance?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "はい。ファッションモデルはランウェイの途中で\n立ち止まってポーズを取りますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. Fashion models pause and\nstrike a pose in the middle of the runway.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "私にはどんなポーズが似合うか研究していたんです\nでも実際にやってみると難しいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was researching which poses suit me best.\nBut it's difficult when I actually try it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "どうすれば自分をより魅力的に見せられるのか……\n考えれば考えるほど深みにはまりそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How can I make myself more attractive…\nThe more I think about it‚ the more I get tangled up in it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それならアイドルの経験を生かしてみたらどうだ？\n自分を魅力的に見せるのはアイドルの基本だろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In that case‚ why not utilize your experience as an idol?\nMaking yourself look attractive is the basics of being an idol‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルの経験ですか……そういえばグラビア撮影では\n好きな顔の角度やよくやる定番のポーズがあります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Experience as an idol… In gravure shoots‚\nthere are favorite angles and standard poses we often do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "グラビアで自分を綺麗に見せる演出は\nモデルのポージングでも役に立つかもしれません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The techniques to present myself beautifully in gravure\nmight also be helpful in modeling poses.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ、その通りだ！　それにダンスで鍛えた\n表現力やアピール力もポージングに応用出来るはずだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Exactly! That's it! Moreover‚ the expressive and appealing skills\nyou've honed through dancing can be applied to posing as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "天動さんにはアイドルとして培ってきた\n技術と経験がある！　それを生かすんだ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You have the skills and experience cultivated as an idol!\nLet's make the most of them!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルの経験を生かせばプロのモデルに匹敵する\nパフォーマンスが出来る……そういうことですね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By utilizing my experience as an idol‚ I can perform\nlike a professional model… That's what you mean!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました！　ありがとうございます！\nアイドルの経験を生かしてモデルを必ずやり遂げます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Understood! Thank you very much!\nI will definitely accomplish being a model by leveraging my experience as an idol!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "頼もしいな。これなら明日の\nモデル事務所との合同練習も期待出来そうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're reliable. With this‚ we can expect tomorrow's joint practice\nwith the modeling agency to go well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "プロのファッションモデルと一緒に練習出来る\n貴重な機会ですから、しっかり勉強してきます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a precious opportunity to practice with\nprofessional fashion models‚ so I'll study hard and",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルでもプロのモデルにひけを取らないことを\n証明してきます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "make sure I don't fall behind even as an idol.\nI'll prove that!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The next day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.9666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1299.999999999983,
          "startTime": 144.2666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-evening",
      "startTime": 144
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "ただいま戻りました……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm back…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様\nモデルとの合同練習はどうだった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Welcome back.\nHow was the joint practice with the models?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-rui016.m4a",
      "text": "そのことでお話があります。……お願いします！\n今日から私の練習時間を倍にして下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have something to talk about… Please listen!\nPlease double my practice time starting today!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "急にどうしたんだ！？　何かあったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What happened all of a sudden!? Is something wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-rui017.m4a",
      "text": "今日、モデルのみなさんのウォーキングを生で見て\n自分の未熟さを思い知らされました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today‚ I saw the models' walk live\nand realized my own immaturity.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-rui018.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルの経験があるくらいでファッションモデルを\n出来る気になっていた自分が恥ずかしいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm embarrassed that I thought I could be a fashion model\njust because I have experience as an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-rui019.m4a",
      "text": "私なんてウォーキングどころかよちよち歩きです\n全然、お話にもならないレベルです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can't even walk properly‚ let alone do a walk.\nIt's not even worth mentioning!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そこまで自信を失うなんて一体何があったんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What happened to make you lose so much confidence?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-rui020.m4a",
      "text": "私はランウェイでいかに美しく歩くかと\nそればかり考えていました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was only thinking about how to walk\nbeautifully on the runway.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 194.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-rui021.m4a",
      "text": "ですがウォーキングはただ歩くだけじゃないんです\nショーには意図やストーリーがあって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But walking is not just about walking.\nThere's intention and story in the show…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 202,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-rui022.m4a",
      "text": "モデルは限られた短い時間の中で\n身振りや歩き方だけでそれら全てを表現するんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Models express all of that with gestures\nand walking in a limited amount of time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 208.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-rui023.m4a",
      "text": "それがどれほどハイレベルな技術か\n実際に目の当たりにして痛感しました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I realized how high-level that skill is\nwhen I actually saw it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 216.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに凄かったのか……\n俺の方こそ何も知らなくてすまなかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Was it that amazing…\nI'm sorry for not knowing anything about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 223.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-rui024.m4a",
      "text": "それだけじゃありません。グラビアの要領で\nポージングをしたらきつく叱られました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not all. When I posed like in gravure shoots‚\nI was scolded harshly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 229.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-rui025.m4a",
      "text": "「それは自分を魅力的に見せるポーズで\nファッションをアピールするポーズじゃない！」って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"That's a pose that makes YOU look attractive\"\n\"It's not a pose for promoting fashion!\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 236.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-rui026.m4a",
      "text": "ファッションショーは服が主役なのに\n私は服よりも自分が目立とうとしてしまった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In a fashion show‚ the clothes are the main focus‚\nbut I ended up trying to stand out more than the clothes…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 243.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-rui027.m4a",
      "text": "最初から私は何もかも間違っていたんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was wrong about everything from the beginning!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 248.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "（今までの経験が通用しなかったことが）\n（そんなにショックだったのか……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Her past experience wasn't applicable…)\n(and that make her's so shocked…)",
