      },
      "startTime": 285.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-rui032.m4a",
      "text": "モデルを一から勉強し直して\nこの仕事をきちんとやり遂げたいんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to study modeling from scratch\nI want to fulfill this job properly!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 292.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "（完璧を目指す意識の高さは天動さんの長所だ）\n（自分の仕事にそれだけプライドを持っているんだ）",
